<title type="html"><![CDATA[The Ruling on Masturbation During the Day in Ramadhaan]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=518&amp;p=558#p558"><![CDATA[
<strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Q: A young man masturbated during the day in Ramadhaan while he was fasting, what is it that is binding upon him to do?</span></strong><br /><br />A: Masturbating during the day in Ramadhan invalidates (his) fast if he did it intentionally and expelled the sperm (i.e. ejaculated). If the fast was an obligatory one he must make that day up and repent to Allah Subhaanahu wa Ta’aala because masturbation is not permitted whether one is fasting or not. (This act of masturbation) is what the people call the secret habit.<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #FF0000">Author:</span></strong> Imaam Bin Baaz<br /><span style="color: #FF0000"><strong>Translator:</strong></span> Abu ‘Abdis Salaam Al Juyaanee<br /><strong>Taken from</strong> Majmoo’a Fataawa wa Maqaalaat Mutanawwi’ah Vol. 15<br /><strong><span style="color: #FF0000">Source:</span></strong> <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.salafyink.com/rulingmasturbationramadhaan/">http://www.salafyink.com/rulingmasturbationramadhaan/</a><!-- m --><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=56">Shehzad Sattar</a> — Tue Oct 18, 2016 11:46 pm</p><hr />
